- Pure/I/O split is genuinely clean: `tools/pipeline/cost.ts` has no fs dependency.
- Null-dollar handling is honest: unknown costs are excluded from cap totals but surfaced in summaries (operator sees "X unknown-cost invocations" alongside the dollar total). No silent zero-cost fallback.
- Cap-crossed event ordering for run/day paths is well-structured (event before abort).

